CatDescriptText: A man and a woman stand at a bar and drink Coca-Cola.  Behind the bar is an advertisement for Coca-Cola in bottles featuring accordion player Graham W. Jackson.  The man is holding a cigarette and a newspaper with headlines "Estes Kefauver" and "Fifth Ward Dropped Mrs. L. Russel..."  The wallpaper has a playing card theme, with hearts, diamonds, clubs, and spades.
TitMainTitle: Man and woman holding Coca Cola bottles, standing at counter in bar or restaurant interior with Coca Cola advertisement with accordion player Graham Jackson, playing card wallpaper, and newspaper with headline "Fifth Ward drops...Mrs. L. Russell"
